anguage file</li>\n	<li>Updated : Plugin Framework</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.0.5 - Released on Jan 11, 2016 </h4>\n<ul>\n    <li>Added: Compatibility with YITH WooCommerce Request a Quote</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.0.4 - Released on Jan 07, 2016 </h4>\n<ul>\n    <li>Updated: Plugin core framework</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.0.3 - Released on Oct 30, 2015 </h4>\n<ul>\n    <li>Added: Support to WooCommerce 2.4</li>\n    <li>Updated: Plugin core framework 2.0</li>\n    <li>Added: Italian language file</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.0.0 - Released on May 15, 2015 </h4>\n<ul>\n    <li>Initial Release</li>\n</ul>\n\n    \";}','no');
